{"word":"G4015 - περιαστράπτω - periastráptō - per-ee-as-trap'-to - Shine round","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιαστράπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>periastráptō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-as-trap'-to"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Shine round"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுற்றிப்பிரகாசி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to flash around, to shine about"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G797 - ἀστράπτω - astráptō - as-trap'-to/797\">G797</a>; to <i>flash</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>envelop in light:</i> - shine round (about)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}